          <title>Sengun records triple-double, VanVleet scores 28 in Rockets 143-107 rout of Bulls</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Fred VanVleet scored a season-high 28 points, Alperen Sengun had 20 points, 11 rebounds and 11 assists for his second triple-double this season and the Houston Rockets routed the Chicago Bulls 143-107 on Sunday night for their fifth straight win.]]></description>
